activities.name: Stage 1 - Tour de Zwift
activities.description:
Ahhhh managed to hold onto peloton for the first 20km until the big hill. Crazy how you give the group even just 10m gap even on an big hill and it’s impossible to catch back up again 😩😩

After being dropped my dreams of a podium finish were over. For the rest of the race I was battling for 39th place. We were yo-yo-ing back and forth for last 10km of the race until I let him take a little lead and with 250m to go I dropped a lifetime best 15 second power to secure that sweet top 40 finish 😂
